            <description><![CDATA[
              <h1>Habitat Version 0.1 Beta 14</h1>
              <h4>What's New & Improved</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Improved: Trackpad thirds window gesture is now less sensitive.</li>
                <li>Fixed: Nook presenting itself when it wasn’t hovered over or menubar was clicked anywhere sometimes.</li>
                <li>Fixed: Hoo Monitor tab loading times and some performance issues.</li>
                <li>Fixed: Some language localization issues.</li>
              </ul>
              <p>More to come.<br><br>
              — Thank you for all the support & feedback!</p>
